=== 2013-现今：签约唱片并筹办专辑 ===
2013年4月11日，她与[[:en:Syco_Music|合成音乐]]和[[:en:Hollywood_Records|好莱坞唱片]]签约，这也是2家唱片公司首度合作的范例。<ref>{{cite web |author=1 years |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/earshot/x-factor-alum-beatrice-miller-437933 |title='X Factor' Alum Beatrice Miller Inks Record Deal |publisher=Hollywood Reporter |date=2013-11-04 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2016-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114151235/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/earshot/x-factor-alum-beatrice-miller-437933 |dead-url=no }}</ref>米勒目前忙于制作将于2014年发售的首张专辑。她正与Autumn Rowe密切合作中。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://twicsy.com/i/U58MBe |title=BeatriceMBR : Bea e Autumn Rowe |publisher=Twicsy |date=2013年12月10日 |accessdate=2014年6月26日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225173448/http://twicsy.com/i/U58MBe |archive-date=2014年2月25日 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>在美版《X音素》刚落幕后不久，米勒将自己的名字缩为碧·米勒(Bea Miller)。<ref>{{cite web |author=Facebook Twitter Instagram YouTube Bea Miller BeaMiller.com |url=http://www.hollywoodrecords.com/artists/bea-miller/ |title=Bea Miller |publisher=Hollywood Records |date= |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140818053203/http://www.hollywoodrecords.com/artists/bea-miller/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>她的首张专辑连同主打歌曲原先预计将于春季发售，约在3-5月间的样子。在专辑制作的同时，她也在[[Instagram|Instagram]]上分享了制作过程中的一些照片，展示了她所用的设备。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://instagram.com/p/jMtxQ7MaYj/ |title=Instagram |publisher=Instagram |date= |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018160938/http://instagram.com/p/jMtxQ7MaYj/ |archive-date=2014-10-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>她曾在[[YouTube|YouTube]]提前上传了尚未正式发售的新歌"[[:en:Rich_Kids_(Bea_Miller_song)|Rich Kids]]"。仅在1周内，就达到了1万5千的观看量。米勒打算在今年夏季推出迷你专辑，并在晚些时候推出完整版专辑。<ref>{{cite web |author=Username * |url=https://www.fanlala.com/news/bea-miller-kicks-month-surprises-rich-kids-teaser |title=Bea Miller Kicks Off a Month of Surprises with "Rich Kids" Teaser |publisher=Fanlala.com |date= |accessdate=2014-04-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140509021840/http://www.fanlala.com/news/bea-miller-kicks-month-surprises-rich-kids-teaser |archivedate=2014-05-09 }}</ref>她发布过首先名为"[[:en:Enemy_Fire|Enemy Fire]]"的新歌片段<ref>{{cite web|url=http://instagram.com/p/mGeZpOMaf8/ |title=Instagram |publisher=Instagram |date= |accessdate=2014-04-30}}</ref>，这首"Enemy Fire"于4月在其官方[[Vevo|Vevo]]频道首播。[[:en:busbee|busbee]]、[[:en:Jarrad_Rogers|Jarrad Rogers]]及[[:en:Mike_Del_Rio|Mike Del Rio]]等艺人参与了她的专辑的制作。2014年4月22日，她发售了首张迷你专辑《年轻的血》("[[:en:Young_Blood_(EP)|Young Blood]]")<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/BeaMiller/status/455059576971227137 |title=Twitter / BeaMiller: my EP comes out on iTunes April 22nd |publisher=Twitter.com |date=2014-04-12 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2015-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911034920/https://twitter.com/beamiller/status/455059576971227137 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.facebook.com/BeaMiller/photos/a.359659354050554.108511.249358218414002/840456569304161/?type=1&theater |title=Bea Miller - Tijdlijnfoto's |publisher=Facebook |date= |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2015-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212151022/https://www.facebook.com/BeaMiller/photos/a.359659354050554.108511.249358218414002/840456569304161/?type=1&theater |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及主打歌曲"[[:en:Dracula_(song)|Dracula]]"。这张EP曾在[[iTunes|iTunes]]流行音乐专辑榜上上升到了第2位。

